snippet.title: Santa's busy day | OFFICIAL TRAILER 2023 | Whishlist now on steam
snippet.description:
December 23th, Santa's busy day will be released on steam!

Whishlist now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2723640/Santas_busy_day/

Can you help Santa deliver his presents as fast as possible?
Join the challenge.

Fly over the roofs and try to hit the houses with your presents. The game will speed up and it gets progressively harder.
